## Create Picked Custom Field

```http
POST https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/picked-custom-fields HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Token token=abc123abc123
X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>

{
  "data": {
    "type": "picked-custom-fields",
    "attributes": {
      "value": "2019-08-28T18:56:53+02:00",
    },
    "relationships": {
      "custom-field": {
        "data": {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "custom-fields",
        },
      },
      "owner": {
        "data": {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "candidates",
        },
      },
    },
  },
}
```

```shell
curl -X "POST" "https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/picked-custom-fields" \
     -H "Authorization: Token token=abc123abc123" \
     -H "X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>"
     -H "Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json" \
     -d '{
   "data": {
     "type": "picked-custom-fields",
     "attributes": {
       "value": "2019-08-28T18:56:53+02:00",
     },
     "relationships": {
       "custom-field": {
         "data": {
           "id": 4,
           "type": "custom-fields",
         },
       },
       "owner": {
         "data": {
           "id": 1,
           "type": "candidates",
         },
       },
     },
   },
}'
```

